title: DDFP 492: Week 3 recap & CB-WR matchups with Terence Newman
itunes:title: DDFP 492: Week 3 recap & CB-WR matchups with Terence Newman
description:
Shek is joined by Ike Taylor and Maurice Jones-Drew in a special debate edition of 'The Hurry Up' to discuss Dak Prescott vs. Carson Wentz and the Broncos' defense vs. the Vikings' defense. Then, the guys break down the best wins and worst losses from Week 3, highlighting the Eagles' win and the Jets' loss. Also, the guys talk to Vikings CB Terence Newman about Sam Bradford, Stefon Diggs and some of the most controversial CB-WR matchups. Plus, in this week's "Time Machine Football," the guys review the 2013 Week 9 game between the Bengals and Dolphins in anticipation of Thursday Night Football.
